message.en_US: What?\. We've got some sweet moves!\. Triblader is the coolest class!
Oh really?\! More like the token generic sword guy that every game seems to have.
Well what do you do?\!\. You fight with a deck of cards!\! That's pretty lame!
And I never see you guys do anything cool either!
I agree.\. All I ever see you guys use is that lame \c[3]Magic Missile\c[0] attack.
Come on, now it's our turn to show off!
Wow, I've never seen a Hexacast do that before!
You guys had this up your sleeve this whole time?
And yet you insist on only using \c[3]Magic Missile\c[0]?!
Well, this is us when we actually try!
